he sings, plays lute and thin whistle, some of his teachers said he'd become the next headmaster of the bardic college. Then the black shakes swept over his beloved city of Cilorealon, wiping out more than half the population. Priests, mages, sages, herbalists, alchemists, they were all unable to find a cure. When he became ill, he thought he was done for. But then, miracle. He became better where so many had died without rhyme or reason, it must have been divine intervention. The others sent him off to find the cure at the massive mages college of the humans to the south.